Package ai.seitok.flow

The root package containing the bare essentials to getting started

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Flow
    The interface for working with command arguments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Faucet
    Controls integration within an application.
    StringFlow
    An extremely simple String-array based Flow implementation
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FlowEmptyException
    FlowEmptyException is thrown when a Flow is empty (hence its name)
    FlowException
    General exception thrown when arguments can't be interpreted
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    FlowCommand
    Tags a method as being a "command method".
    FlowSplitCommand
    Tags a method as being a "command method" that is split into multiple sub-commands.
